lor><br>Damage: 375 \\u00d7 6 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 2,640<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbDispels Buffs<br>\\u30fbFreeze<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 6 seconds<br><\/div><\/dd><dt\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/944f49691bf38a5e905697ff03d017ad2.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Bon App\\u00e9tit<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Applies one of the following effects to the entire<br>team based on the user\'s current cooking stance:<br><br>Appetizer Stance: Increases defense,<br>increases inspiration by two stages,<br>and increases flame resistance.<br><br>Entr\\u00e9e Stance: Increases critical rate,<br>increases inspiration by three stages,<br>and fills the skill gauge for Amuse-bouche<br>by 50%.<br><br>Dessert Stance: Increases strength,<br>increases inspiration by two stages, and<br>increases the modifier applied to damage<br>against flame-attuned enemies.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\"><color=#00008B>During Appetizer Stance:<\/color><br>Skill Energy Required: 10,595<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbDefense +25%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 15 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Does not stack<br>\\u30fbFlame Res +20%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 30 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Does not stack<br>\\u30fbInspiration Level +2<br>\\u3000\\u3000Charges: 1<br><br><color=#00008B>During Entr\\u00e9e Stance:<\/color><br>Skill Energy Required: 10,595<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbCritical Rate +18%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 15 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Does not stack<br>\\u30fbInspiration Level +3<br>\\u3000\\u3000Charges: 1<br><br><color=#00008B>During Dessert Stance:<\/color><br>Skill Energy Required: 10,595<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbStrength +15%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 15 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Does not stack<br>\\u30fbInspiration Level +2<br>\\u3000\\u3000Charges: 1<br>\\u30fbWater-Attuned Damage +15%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 15 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Does not stack<br><\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/87595b7438e74e5502d8b830d6bd16832.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Strength +10%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIncreases strength by 10%.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Chain Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/2eacc0ecdcae8474365161935d0e38232.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>(Water) Above 10 Hits = Flame Res +10%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIf a team member is attuned to Water: <br>reduces flame damage taken by them by 10%<br>when the combo count is 10 or higher.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n<div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/cc3f28b7bfce6dfc1ea65f36822cae7f2.png\\"><\/span><span>Dutiful Chef<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Increases attack rate by 10% for 20 seconds each<br>time one of the user\'s attacks is a critical hit.<br>After activating, this effect will not activate again<br>for 10 seconds.<br><br>In addition, using a skill will grant the user a<br>strength amp with a maximum team amp level<br>of two. After this amp is granted, this ability<br>will not grant it again for 10 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/c0b3ec2bdf2af0f73ef2627b87da47152.png\\"><\/span><span>Potent Burn Res +100%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to burning by 100%.<br>When the user is hit by an attack that would have<br>inflicted burning on them, their strength is increased<br>by 15% for 10 seconds. After activating, this buff will<br>not activate again for 15 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/9313ae9aa920e91dfb0863136ae5dc042.png\\"><\/span><span>Combo Time +5<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Extends the window between hitting an enemy and<br>the combo counter resetting by five seconds.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. The stats shown here represent the adventurer at level 100 with 70 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>2. The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities.<\/div><div>3. The stats for the adventurer included in this notification shown in any prior notifications or preview videos were the stats at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>4. When an adventurer&#39;s skill level increases, the skill gauge will fill more slowly when set as a shared skill.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1649138400,"prev_article_id":"2922","next_article_id":"3286","image_path":"","update_time":1649121373}}}'